metadata.name: Acrona
metadata.description:
Acrona : 

“ Dex want to destroy a whole world to build a new one. Our lives meant a dime to him! All the sacrifices we done! The sacrifice i fucking did! 
His thirst for power made him blind, if to die for a good cause, for this cause so imma fucking do it. i'm not playing a hero thing , but we matter! We fucking matter Boxxy! “
